
DEUS, qui per sanctum Joséphum Confessórem tuum, ad erudiéndam spíritu intelligéntiæ ac pietátis juventútem, novum Ecclésiæ tuæ subsídium providére dignátus es: præsta, quæsumus; nos, ejus exémplo et intercessióne, ita fácere et docére, ut præmia consequámur ætérna. Per Dóminum.
O GOD, who, for training the youth in the spirit of piety and understanding, didst by means of blessed Joseph thy Confessor vouchsafe to provide thy Church with a new help; grant, we beseech thee, that, by his example and intercession, we may so act and teach as to obtain an eternal reward. Through our Lord.
